<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Abundant in much of Paraguay, the Chiquitania of Bolivia, parts of southern Brazil and Misiones in Argentina but scattered and less common elsewhere in Argentina, Bolivia, Uruguay and Brazil. We have not traced the record from Peru (Austin and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Huáman">Huaman</normalizedToken>
(1996), which seems improbable. It is often found in scrub and on forest margins around rock platforms although it is not restricted to this habitat. Its absence from many lowland areas is surprising.
